page.title: 06OWTON MANOR
page.content:
{Owton Manor Mainly all the houses are council houses with a few privately owned. There are flats and houses,the houses all having{3}bedrooms and all have small front and back gardens.The windows are flush with the outside wall. Almost all of the houses are terraced,some having{2}bedrooms.The houses were built in the mid 1950's ,and some of them need modernisation.
{Fens These houses are between{7}to{20 years old. The oldest being from Kesteven Road to the Fens shops.South Fens being the most recently built.They all have modern central heating systems.
